{
  "stem": "1918.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 254.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the destruction of the Hungarian Jews was not only the swiftest, but Auschwitz, I understood then, from the kapo who spoke to me, that in all the years, the few people who survived for several years-- some Slovak girl.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Her name was Rozsika.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was a very beautiful girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she perished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she told me that in all the years that she survived in Auschwitz, she has never seen such carnage as when the Hungarian Jews were brought in.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Instead of burning 10,000 people a day, it could be as many as from 10,000 to 24,000 a day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the brutality and the carnage was at a higher-- you know, more highly developed than any other time previously.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You probably know that I have written some books, and these stories are in my books.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of the stories is of how on March 19, my youngest sister, Potyo, was sitting in a little room which we called the pink room.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on the table, there was a radio.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no television in those days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was listening, and she knew all of the programs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And particularly, she knew all of the programs because she was already kicked out of school because she had an operation of-- what is it you have in  your--",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Appendix.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was out those days for six weeks from school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they wouldn't take her back when she was ready to return.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the poor child was condemned to listen to the radio all the time because she couldn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was-- she was listening Sunday afternoon on March 19 to the radio.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And suddenly she said, hey, everybody listen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's something wrong.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
